.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-CLEAN" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.1.17" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-clean \- Remove old tracked job directories
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose clean [OPTIONS]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Remove old tracked job directories under .hpc\-compose for the compose file while keeping recent tracking data available.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB-f\fR, \fB--file\fR \fIFILE\fR
Compose specification file to read. Default: compose.yaml.
.TP
\fB--age\fR \fIDAYS\fR
Remove tracked job directories older than this many days.
.TP
\fB--all\fR
Remove all tracked job directories except the latest one.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose clean \-f compose.yaml \-\-age 7
hpc\-compose clean \-f compose.yaml \-\-all
.fi
